title: Provided further that in case of composite redevelopment undertaken as mention in (a) & (b) above for two or more but not more than five plots of tenant occupied buildings the incentive FSI shall be 60% & the occupier shall be eligible for 8% additional rehab carpet area and for plots six or more then incentive shall be 70% and the occupier shall be eligible for 15 % additional rehab carpet area
